{"lemma":"حَمِيل","slug":"حَمِيل","root":"ح.م.ل","root_slug":"ح-م-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-م-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n9179"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AD%D9%8E%D9%85%D9%90%D9%8A%D9%84"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n9179","headword_ar":"حَمِيلٌ","root":"Hml","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHomuwlN","text_ar":"مَحْمُولٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Borne, carried, taken up and carried, conveyed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"carried off"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"away"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Msb, K.) ―         -b2-  Hence, (Msb,) The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rubbish,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rotten leaves, and scum, that are borne"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a torrent. (S, Msb, K. *) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thing"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aYo'","text_ar":"شَىْء"},{"kind":"text","text":", accord. to copies of the K and the TA, but accord. to the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saboY","text_ar":"سَبْى"},{"kind":"text","text":", agreeably with the next of the explanations here following,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is carried from one country or town to another"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"among a party of captives."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A captive;"},{"kind":"text","text":"because carried from one country or town to another. (Msb.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"One who is carried a child from his country, not born in"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the territory of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"El-Islám:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one who is carried from his country to the country of El-Islám:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a child with a woman who carries it, and says that it is her son:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any relation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"kinsman, in the territory of the enemy:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one that is carried from the territory of the unbelievers to that of ElIslám, and who is therefore not allowed to inherit without evidence:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Th, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a child in the belly of his mother when taken from the land of the unbelievers."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A foundling,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"child cast out by his mother, whom persons carry off and rear:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) in some copies of the K,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fayarivuwnahu","text_ar":"فَيَرِثُونَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is erroneously put for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fayurab~uwnahu","text_ar":"فَيُرَبُّونَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b7-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"One whose origin,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lineage, is suspected;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who claims for his father one who is not;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who is claimed as a son by one who is not his father;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daEiY~N","text_ar":"دَعِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, Msb, K.) ―         -b8-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A stranger:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) as being likened to [the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hamiyl","text_ar":"حَمِيل"},{"kind":"text","text":"of] the torrent, or to the child in the belly. (Er-Rághib, TA.) ―         -b9-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"One who is responsible,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a surety,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K,) for ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bi","text_ar":"بِ"},{"kind":"text","text":") a debt or a bloodwit; as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAmilN","text_ar":"حَامِلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:) because he bears [or is burdened with] the obligation, together with him upon whom the obligation properly rests. (TA.) ―         -b10-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What is withered and black"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vumaAm","text_ar":"ثُمَام"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wa$iyj","text_ar":"وَشِيج"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaEap","text_ar":"ضَعَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tariyfap","text_ar":"طَرِيفَة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b11-  (assumed tropical:)  The ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thong called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iraAk","text_ar":"شِرَاك"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a sandal"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (O, K.) In one copy of the K,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$ryk","text_ar":"الشريك"},{"kind":"text","text":"is put in the place of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$rAk","text_ar":"الشراك"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Msb","K","TA","S","O","Mgh","Th"]}]}}